The quiet cul-de-sac street has the beauty of country living but only a couple minutes to the convenience of I-65. The all Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring means easy to clean and maintain, while the style of things like the Barn door to the main bedroom! Come take a look at this wonderful home today!
